edu.udel.cis.taschd.assign

Class Assignment

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.udel.cis.taschd.assign.Assignment

  • public class Assignment
extends java.lang.Object

    An Assignment is a mapping of CourseAssistants to course Sections. This specifies the sections assigned to each CA. It hides the details of the internal representation of this mapping. Methods to construct, modify, display, and read assignments are provided.

    Assignment uses modules ca and course.
